<exploration xml:id="warm-cuantosVes-diferentesArreglosDe4" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude"> 

<title>Cuántos ves: Diferentes arreglos de 4</title>

<statement>
  <p>
    <line>¿Cuántos ves?</line>
    <line>¿Cómo lo sabes?, ¿qué ves?</line>
  </p>
  <sidebyside>  
    <image source="svg-source/tikz-file-136327">
      <shortdescription>4 puntos.</shortdescription>
    </image>
    <image source="svg-source/tikz-file-158684">
      <shortdescription>4 puntos.</shortdescription>
    </image>
    <image source="svg-source/tikz-file-141785">
      <shortdescription>4 puntos.</shortdescription>
    </image> 
  </sidebyside>
</statement>

<solution>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <p>Sample responses:</p>
<ul>
      <li>4: I counted 1, 2, 3, 4. There are 2 and 2 more.</li>
      <li>4: I see 3 on top and 1 more on the bottom. I see 2 and then 2 more.</li>
      <li>4: It is just like the last picture but the dots are all in a line. 1 dot is missing from the 5-frame.</li>
    </ul>
  </solution>


